Cape Town Five suspects were arrested on Monday after paramedics were robbed at gunpoint while assisting a heart attack patient in Heideveld.&#8220;At around 00:30 the paramedics were held at gunpoint by six suspects and robbed of personal effects in Carol Court, Heideveld, while assisting a heart attack patient.&#8221;The suspects were due to make a court appearance in Athlone.http://www.iol.co.za/news/crime-courts/medics-robbed-at-gunpoint-while-helping-heart-attack-patient-9560454